Name: anus lymphoma
Definition: A female reproductive system disease that is characterized by an excessively mobile uterus secondary to lacerations of the broad and cardinal ligaments

Name: malignant anus melanoma
Definition: An ovarian disease that is characterized by irregular or absent ovulation.

Name: anus sarcoma
Definition: A sarcoma and malignant neoplasm of anus that is located_in the anus.
